name: Barbell Shoulder Press
description: 1. Using a barbell with an overhand grip just beyond shoulder width 2 Stand with feet shoulder width aprt forming strong base 3. Begin with the barbell held at shoulder height in front of your body 4. Push the barbell stright up over your head maintaining your torso upright 5. Slowly return the weight to start position and repeat for desired reps
variations: Dumbebell Shoulder Press, Seated Barbell Press
